text: Daniel Natea (born 21 April 1992) is a Romanian judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's +100 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Abdullo Tangriev. ==References== == External links == * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Romania Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Romania
